1. *Nosio* je knjige u torbi. (He carried books in a bag.)
2. *Nosi* li ona knjige? (Does she carry books?)
3. Ona je *noseći* knjige prošla pored mene. (She passed by me, carrying books.)
4. Ona je *nosila* knjige u torbi. (She carried books in a bag.)
5. On je *noseo* knjige do njene kuće. (He carried books to her house.)